content.text:
Photo 1: Photograph of two planes next to each other at an airport. A smaller private jet and a bigger private jet. Caption for photo 1: 'From a smaller plane to a bigger plane - much bigger.'
 Photo 2: A man who appears to be in his fourties holding two luggage bags in front of an open door with lots of luggage at the entrace of a brick building that appears to be the entry to an apartment or a dorm. Caption for Photo 2: 'From what you thought was a huge amount of luggage 
 Photo 3: [three photos in a collage] Boxes of household items being packed into the back of an SUV indicating a moving day. Caption of Photo 3: 'To a truely huge amount of luggage'
